id isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/scope-hong-kongs-new-national-security-laws-2024-03-08/</guid></item><item><title>小鹏汽车AeroHT Voyager X2在广州完成低空飞行</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-xpengs-drone-car-aeroht-voyager-x2-completes-low-altitude-flight-2024-03-08/</link><description>中国电动汽车制造商小鹏汽车的子公司小鹏航空在一份声明中表示，该公司周五表示，其飞行无人机 AeroHT Voyager X2 在南方城市广州的中央商务区完成了低空飞行。</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Mar 2024 10:03:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-xpengs-drone-car-aeroht-voyager-x2-completes-low-altitude-flight-2024-03-08/</guid></item><item><title>中国2月份新增人民币贷款从历史高位回落</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-february-new-yuan-loans-seen-retreating-record-high-2024-03-08/</link><description>路透调查显示，尽管央行寻求刺激疲软的经济增长并应对通货紧缩压力，但由于季节性因素，2月份中国银行贷款可能从1月份的历史高位大幅回落。</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Mar 2024 09:44:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-february-new-yuan-loans-seen-retreating-record-high-2024-03-08/</guid></item><item><title>台湾敦促中国不要改变前线岛屿附近海域的局势</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/taiwan-urges-china-not-change-status-quo-around-waters-near-kinmen-islands-2024-03-08/</link><description>台湾最高决策机构周五敦促中国不要通过派遣海警船进入禁区来改变台湾前线岛屿附近海域的“现状”，称紧张局势应该是“可控的”。</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Mar 2024 08:34:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/taiwan-urges-china-not-change-status-quo-around-waters-near-kinmen-islands-2024-03-08/</guid></item><item><title>收购目标 Currys 表示希腊资产处置将于四月完成</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/takeover-target-currys-says-greek-disposal-will-complete-april-2024-03-08/</link><description>处于潜在收购战中心的英国电器零售商 Currys 周五表示，在获得希腊当局批准后，出售其希腊子公司的交易将于 4 月上半月完成。</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Mar 2024 07:41:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/takeover-target-currys-says-greek-disposal-will-complete-april-2024-03-08/</guid></item><item><title>中国称印度在喜马拉雅边境增兵不会缓解紧张局势</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/more-indian-troops-border-wont-ease-tensions-says-china-foreign-ministry-2024-03-08/</link><description>外交部发言人周五表示，中国认为印度在有争议的边境增兵的举动“不利于缓解紧张局势”。</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Mar 2024 07:39:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/more-indian-troops-border-wont-ease-tensions-says-china-foreign-ministry-2024-03-08/</guid></item><item><title>第23条：香港新国安法你需要了解的事</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/article-23-what-you-need-know-about-hong-kongs-new-national-security-laws-2024-03-08/</link><description>经过上周结束的为期一个月的公众咨询后，香港政府于周五公布了拟议的国家安全法案。市领导希望该法案能够迅速获得通过，可能在几周内获得通过。</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Mar 2024 07:36:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/article-23-what-you-need-know-about-hong-kongs-new-national-security-laws-2024-03-08/</guid></item><item><title>MH370：10 年来我们对马来西亚航空飞机的了解</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/malaysias-missing-mh370-plane-what-we-know-10-years-2024-03-08/</link><description>十年前，载有 239 名乘客的马来西亚航空公司 MH370 航班失踪，至今仍然是世界上最大的航空谜团之一。</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Mar 2024 06:54:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/malaysias-missing-mh370-plane-what-we-know-10-years-2024-03-08/</guid></item><item><title>亚洲股市因中国改革和人工智能激增而吸引大量外国资金</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/asian-stocks-draw-massive-foreign-funds-chinas-reforms-ai-surge-2024-03-08/</link><description>随着北京推出改革措施以及人工智能（AI）热潮推动科技股飙升，中国股市出现反弹，外国投资者在二月份向亚洲股市注入了大量资金。</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Mar 2024 06:41:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/asian-stocks-draw-massive-foreign-funds-chinas-reforms-ai-surge-2024-03-08/</guid></item><item><title>1-2月中国电动汽车销量放缓；降价力度加大</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-ev-sales-slow-january-february-competition-intensifies-2024-03-08/</link><description>周五的行业数据显示，中国电动汽车销量在今年头几个月放缓，随着市场领导者比亚迪带头进行更大幅度的降价，竞争加剧。</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Mar 2024 05:35:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-ev-sales-slow-january-february-competition-intensifies-2024-03-08/</guid></item><item><title>打拳抽铁，中国女子走“YOLO”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/lifestyle/punching-pumping-iron-chinese-women-go-yolo-2024-03-08/</link><description>一名 30 多岁的女性没有工作、没有朋友，也没有人生方向，她决定开始打拳击，引发了身体上的转变，这是今年中国票房最高的电影的故事。</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Mar 2024 05:32:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/lifestyle/punching-pumping-iron-chinese-women-go-yolo-2024-03-08/</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，中国恒大清算人任命法律顾问</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/china-evergrande-liquidators-appoint-legal-advisers-sources-say-2024-03-08/</link><description>据直接了解情况的消息人士透露，中国恒大的清算人已聘请三家律师事务所就这家陷入困境的房地产巨头的清盘程序提供咨询。</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Mar 2024 05:20:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/china-evergrande-liquidators-appoint-legal-advisers-sources-say-2024-03-08/</guid></item></channel></rss>